window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>I sold my soul to the devil only to turn around and slit his throat…</p> <p>Thomas Kincaid took everything from me. My mother. My hopes. My innocence.</p> <p>Now, it’s my turn.</p> <p>He thought he was safe.</p> <p>They all did.</p> <p>They were wrong.</p> <p>Men always think they can take without ever having to deal with the consequences. Well, now I’m back, and I'm the last consequence they’ll ever see.</p> <p>*This is a dark romance, and contains dark themes which some listeners may find uncomfortable or upsetting. If you do not enjoy these themes, or have triggers, please do not listen. Recommended for 18+ due to sexual content and adult situations. Please listen responsibly.*</p>"; 
